data.description: Views of the Catalina's, Tortolito's and Hole #15 just don't end on this 2674 sq. ft. Vienta Elevation C floor plan with a large Hobby Room and large extended Garage for your Golf Cart.  This Premiere Series home has 2 Bdrm Suites and 2 Baths plus Powder Room; both Bdrms have Walk-in Closets.  The primary Bath has a 42'' X 60'' Shower and built-in Seats.  The chef's Kitchen has Quartz counters; a Walk-in Pantry; Gas Cooktop; and a true Entertainer's Kitchen Island.  Off the kitchen is the large Great Room featuring a Media Alcove.  The Dining area is perfect for your entertainment needs.  The spacious Den can be used as a 3rd Bdrm for guests.  All rooms feature 9', 10' & 11' ceiling heights to make the house feel even more roomy.  Patio has 378 sq. ft. of Covered Living Space that look south down the fairway toward the mountains.  This home leaves little to be desired.  Begin or continue your Arizona experience in the perfect home.
